        </span>
                    <div class="caption">
            Industrial firms employees manufacture Personal Protective Equipment (PPE), like face shields, to supply New York's health care workers and hospitals at the Brooklyn Navy Yard on March 26, 2020 in New York City.             <span class="attribution"></span>
